Package: togolab.scrna
Title: Single-Cell and -Omics Analysis Helpers for the Togo Lab
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ye Ji", "Choi", email = "yejichoi@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Togo Lab", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Single-cell RNA-seq and downstream -omics analysis helpers for the
    Bjornstad-Pyle-Tommerdahl (Togo) lab: NEBULA differential expression,
    feature UMAPs, cell-type composition, GSEA/pathway tools, volcano plots,
    and Slingshot trajectory inference. Companion to the lightweight 'togolab'
    core package; heavy analysis dependencies are isolated here.
